{"title":"莲花礼赞","authors":["曾维松"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲花礼赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾维松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲花在南风中歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高扬的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞动世纪雷霆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从历史黑洞里翩跹而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投入母亲的堤岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回归的国土，灿烂微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺拔的莲花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合拢几个世纪的愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁的憧憬鲜花一般开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁的眸子今天神采飞扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二万万个声音叫着你的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圣洁的莲花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着芬芳的花径"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪如星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在血液中流淌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒发冲冠的诗人走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的《七子之歌》植根我们心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦涩的莲子心啊，深情呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“母亲！我要回来，母亲！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立东方的伟人也走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他博大精深思想的海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲叶碧连天，孕育着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孕育着一抹含苞欲放花朵的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲花，一种非凡的美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是游子的相思是骨肉的企盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相携相依啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬勃的花瓣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与鲜艳的五星红旗一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猎猎飘扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：湖南冷水江制碱厂）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}